comments: Mrs. Yount is an absolute gem! She is the sweetest lady and will do anything to help you better understand and learn. She actually wants to get to know each and every person which is pretty cool. She does a lot of quizzes, so each one doesn\'t count for very much. 1 test, some presentations, quizzes, and an optional final--show up and you have an A!

I absolutely adore this woman. She\'s incredible and truly interested in her students. Very easy A if you come to class, and it\'s a very very interesting class! She\'s an amazing teacher and is always there to help. I definitely recommend this class! Loved it!

Mrs. Yount makes learning ASL fun and enjoyable. She was truly interested in the success of her students. Very little to no note taking in class. There was a book, but we never used it. I would highly recommend this class to anyone who knows basic sign language. Easy A if you make the effort to be in class and participate!
